Class AuthServiceImpl

java.lang.Object
com.peaslimited.shoppeas.service.implementation.AuthServiceImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
AuthService
@Service public class AuthServiceImpl extends Object implements AuthService
Implementation of the AuthService interface, providing methods for registering and updating consumers and wholesalers through the RegistrationFactory and AuthRepository.
